deviceName.name: deviceName

deviceMinCurMT.description: Display or set device minimum electric current measurement threshold. Example: range 0.0~32.0 represents 0~320. NOTICE: Minimum threshold should be smaller than maximum threshold. Empty value: -3000. If the device does not support this OID, it returns value -2000000.

deviceOutletControl.name: deviceOutletControl
deviceOutletControl.description: This function is used for all outlet ports control. Set off(1) to turn off for all outlet ports. Set on(2) to turn on for all outlet ports. Get this object always return nostatus(3), because there is no device status.

deviceOutletReboot.name: deviceOutletReboot
deviceOutletReboot.description: This function is used for all outlet ports to reboot. Only when outlet status is ON can do outlet reboot action to all ports. Set yes(2) to reboot all outlet ports. Get this object always return no(1).

perportreading.name: perportreading
perportreading.description: Outlet is per-port reading or not.

doorSensorStatus.name: doorSensorStatus
doorSensorStatus.description: Display door sensor status. close(0) represents door close. open(1) represents door open. not-attached(2) represents door sensor don't attach to device.

popThreshold.name: popThreshold
popThreshold.description: (-1)means default value same as Bank Max Current 16 A. Example: range 0.0~32.0 represents 0~320 You can define the POP threshold or set as default(-1) value.
